headline: T. Rowe Price (NASDAQ:TROW) Surprises With Q3 Sales
summary: Investment management firm T. Rowe Price (NASDAQ:TROW) reported Q3 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 6% year on year to $1.89 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.81 per share was 10.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
